    "Elbow swelling",
    "Pain on elbow manipulation",
    "Reluctance to exercise",
    "Stiff gait after rest"
  ],
  "severity": "high",
  "treatment_overview": "Surgical intervention is often recommended to remove bone fragments or reshape joint surfaces. Medical management includes NSAIDs, joint supplements, and physiotherapy.",
